This repository is an unofficial Chinese localization of the Stanford CS231n
Spring 2026 assignment starter code.

Original course page:
https://cs231n.stanford.edu/assignments.html

Original assignment materials are provided by Stanford CS231n and their
respective authors. This repository preserves the starter-code TODO structure
and does not include assignment solutions.

中文说明：
本仓库是 CS231n Spring 2026 作业 starter code 的非官方中文本地化版本，仅用于学习和阅读便利。请遵守原课程的 Honor Code、版权声明和作业协作政策。
